I stole this from Courtney!!

Everything has just been confusing, strange, complicated, and any other word you could think of that just makes everything harder! Not to mention it's FREEZING! and I hate cold weather! I mean everything is just filled with over the top drama! and I can't stand drama, like I try to stay out of it as much as possible..... lately its been drawen to me, and I can't get away fom it!

.:Relationships:.        The main ones!

Kasey and I are the same as always! GREAT! we've pretty much figured out that if we spend too much time together, then we get sick of each other! and thats not a good thing! We normally hang out on weekends, and tell each other pretty much everything from that week, thats worth talking about, and how can I talk about Kasey without talking about Jimmy (in Kasey's words "Babe")! Jimmy... I feel like I can talk to him about ANYTHING and EVERYTHING! and he'll comepletely understand and if its a kind of situation that I get upset, and I start crying, he'll make me laugh soo hard that the tears are from laughing soo hard! Mindi and I..... I don't know how our relationship is now.....I mean we're not in a big drama filled fight, but it's not like we're completely ok, like we were. I'm not mad at her at all!! (and if she doesn't know that, she does now.) I just wish she would of told me that she said 'yes' instead of telling me that she didn't give him a straight answer, But I'm happy for them, really I am! That helped me realize alot! and I thank her for helping without realizing that she was helping. Mike and I....... I don't know excatly what to say about that because with him all I hear from him is "I'm sorry" and "I've been an asshole", and I'm sick of hearing it! so I'm gonna try to not talk to him as much as possible, I know that there are sometimes that I will but I'm gonna keep it to a certian amount. Dani and I, we have an amazing friendship but all we need to do is hang out more! I know I'm then stupid one that doesn't come online and ask her if she wants to hang out more (I would say call her but she's always online so), and I should do that more!! Dani, we need to hang out more!! Lacie and I are becoming really good friends.....and I like it! Usually we get into a fight once a year, but I don't plan and hope that doesn't happen again! I like how close we are now! We should hang out more out of school tho! Maybe we could rent more movies!! Lacie give me a call sometime! Kristy and I.... I don't think Kristy likes me very much. For some reason when ever we're around each other, I feel like, she'd rather I wasn't there or something along those lines. Danielle (Kelly) and I..... have a very funny friendship!! I mean its just soo amusing! She is just soo funny and pretty much everytime I talk to her, I bust out laughing and cry because I'm laughing soo hard! and lastly Kyle and I.....there is only thing in this friendship I wish I could change.... the head-over-heels feeling. Just when I was feeling like I was over him completley, all those feeling come back and rush though my body, so I have all of these feelings of wanting him back and needing him back! but I've realized one feeling, that makes his and Danielle's relationship even harder for me, is that I'm in love with him! Thinking back to 7th grade, I never thought I'd feel this way about him! Ever! and I'm not gonna mess up anything between him and Danielle because I'm not the kind of person to do that.

.:Love Life:.

    I have no Love life!

.:Home Life:.

    My mom and I are actually in the process of moving, We're getting all the paper work together and ready for when we go to my uncle's for Thanksgiving, so everyone can sign them. See my mom isn't the only person that owns our house, my uncles Zip and Tom plus my aunt Polly do to. All of them own this house, and they all have to sign some papers to sell the house. It doesn't sound so bad, but my uncle Zip isn't the most organized guy in the world, he'd sign them, then lose them and forget about them. Plus he's moving, and he doesn't have a cell phone so we can't call him, and can't get to a computer to check his e-mail. Its very frustrating.

Well I'm gonna stop now casue I've been trying to type this thing for 2 hours!! Its hard to type in fake nails!! don't get them!!

Love ya'll,

                                                      ~*Haley

Where do I start...........

4th of July weekend!

I was on Lake George in Michigan. I got sun brunt on my shoulders!! bad!!! I slept on the sofa. My dad decided to be mean and put the dog on the sofa while I was still sleeping and waited for the dog to fall a sleep and take a picture!!! I got pissed...very pissed!!

OHIO

My Dads house was boring. I really think I'm allergic to something at his house. The first week I was there my step-mother, Kristi, took my brother, Hadden, my sister, Shannon, and myself to the city pool called Water Works, while my dad slept. I was laying in the sun most of the time. My dad works 3rd shift which is 12am to 8am.

West Virginia

When I was with my grandparents.....man, they are soo funny! I love them to death! The first day i was there my grandpa decides to go for a drive thru the country on the "back roads", he knows that I fall asleep on long car rides! and he decides to drive thru Virgina and into TENNESSEE!!! He's crazy! My grandma and I made 4 loaves of zuccinni(sp) bread! Theres one in my fridge if anyone wants to try some. I went to 2 family reunions! My great grandma's reuion was on Saterday and I saw soooo many people I hadn't seen in a looonnngg time! Then I had to go to the West reunion (my grandma side)....I only people i knew besides my grandparents was my great aunt Ileane and her husband Clyde. Thats sad!

OHIO

Back in Ohio......pretty much the same...except the day before I came back home, we all went water skiing....man that makes ya hurt the day after!! but it was funn!

MICHIGAN FINALLY

Well I got home Saturday, and went to Riches with Kasey, Mindi, Courtney, and Danielle! It was interesting! very interesting!! I'm sorry Courtney! Let me know when you get ungrounded so we can hang out! Sunday.....was not a every good day for me.... I went to Kasey at around 2 ish and Danielle was there. About an hour later I get a call from Kyle and he broke up with me but i was expecting it... He says it was for family issues....I'd want someone there that somewhat knows what I'm going thru if I were him...but I'm not so...well....Lacie says he'll come back to me when he realizes what he left....but i don't think soo....but ya never know, all I can do is wish.....

I'm gonna go cause I gotta take a shower cause i stink!!

                               ~*Haley*~
